      "Health / Weight Loss / Pharmaceuticals Risk"
    ],
    "readout": "Independent human perception concentrates in Health/Supplements and in advertorial, listicle, and native formats — the same areas the taxonomy prioritizes as health and deceptive-claim risk. Low-perceived-deception categories (journalism, apparel, B2B) are not prioritized. This corroborates the taxonomy's risk ranking at the category level; it is not per-ad enforcement agreement and confers no promotion eligibility."
